Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.97,0:00:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不要一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你還在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司還在我的身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 我在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.45,0:00:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就在這
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪裡都不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.31,0:00:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.12,0:00:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我開動囉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.90,0:00:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會不會覺得我做得比以前好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是每天積累的成果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可是認真做就能做好的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}味道怎麼樣
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂喂 司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你現在是不是非常的想要去看電影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是這樣想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以把這個拿好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是為什麼突然給我這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克很少會給我禮物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是因為啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿來拜託我幫她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我才
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啦你給我收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟艾拉兩個人去開心一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話先說在前頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只是很偶然地拿到了票
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我可是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只好把票讓給很閒的你們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的只是這樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總之謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}噢 司君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這些你不介意的話就收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遊覽地旅館的目錄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要好好地利用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.68,0:04:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我拿到了平時常去的飯店的招待券
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讓給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}店裡有著裝規定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我替你們準備了正裝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是餐時表演的票和加油用品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}粉絲俱樂部的特典裡多放了兩份
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}願意的話就拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你隨時都可以開走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}停車場的地址在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼 你沒有駕照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事沒事有自動駕駛功能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉呢 司君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我每個月的零用錢都好緊張的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我只能給你這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 機會難得 明天要休個假一起去逛逛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是像夢一般的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多虧了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿足了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想做的事還有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好奇心真強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}激情退卻了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要好好的體驗人生才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不然就太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只要能夠獨占你動人的笑容就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要這樣我就滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一次看電影覺得怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到現在還不能平靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:06:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剛才一直握著我的手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.81,0:06:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是因為在黑暗的地方就擔心司會不會忽然不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感到很不安…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}給你添麻煩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的手你再怎麼握都沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 司 我想試試電影裡的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道是膝枕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的膝蓋可以用的…所以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…那就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司的頭髮有點刺人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}超級害羞就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}錯誤 沒有聽清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 錯誤什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其實是聽清楚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我沒聽到喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我最近害怕晚上睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我會去想像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會不會再也醒不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會不會再也見不到司了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是像這樣和司在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那種感覺就咻的消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司好厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可以隨時來依靠我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從大家那裡感覺到超級強的「明天休息吧」的氣場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司想要去玩的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}表情很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然這樣的每一天都很快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是這樣下去身體會遲鈍的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果…在迎接最後一天之前就不能動了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就好討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 不可能有那種事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過 一不小心就開始胡思亂想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那樣的話…果然還是像平常那樣度過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天這樣的日子偶爾過一過就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}數據上沒有什麼顯眼的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太慢了 遲到10分鐘了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}工作太忙了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去準備
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉的數據
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道今天也來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 那倆人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有必要這麼頻繁的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也好 對本人來說能安撫一下情緒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算如此 也沒必要休息日也過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看到他們兩個人就想哭了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 過來一下好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正好我也有事情想問香月姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}希望你把下一個工作交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和艾拉負責的變成只有莎拉小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什… 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉的回收同意書
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}由你來簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你暫時集中關注艾拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}德國洋甘菊是一年生的草本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.90,0:11:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直長著葉子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}種子落下來同時會長出新的芽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放置不管的話會長一大片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有不好的 最好是摘下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這邊的百里香怕熱小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反過來迷迭香很耐熱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是如果不整理的話葉子會太繁茂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下面會枯掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}夏天應該收穫一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉很瞭解藥草呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}研究了很久嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剛開始培育的時候有很多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且只要大家說我泡的茶好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就覺得我能在這裡待著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:12:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還想種些別的看看呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊…不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你這貨在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為現在只有我和艾拉的工作很輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就想著有沒有什麼其他可做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就讓艾拉教我這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最近好像找到竅門了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「找到竅門了」個頭啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我才受不了外行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正好趁這個機會跟你說明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼不去休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你倒是稍微看一下氣氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「咦」個頭啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起來公司上班 你應該多花些時間來陪艾拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算你們不來上班大家也不會抱怨的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們不能休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然滿和大家說的 我們很感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但我和艾拉兩個人做出了決定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就和平常一樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我希望大家能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿 是你輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香月姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你也是對他們一直放心不下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝你 滿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我也想像珍惜和司的時間一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}珍惜在這裡度過的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算了 隨便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了 你們也別看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快回去工作 別偷懶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 待會還有約會要去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小艾拉 能再幫我倒杯茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的 馬上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 現在有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個的簽名 由我來簽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我希望司來簽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:14:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的腦中有時會閃現出一些想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們就這樣逃到遠方會怎樣之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就在想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}該怎樣不告訴任何人然後離開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}給你留下了痛苦的回憶了呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}水柿司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天就是莎拉小姐的回收日了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們兩個負責的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這就是最後一件了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.19,0:16:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}是的 您說的我都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}但是讓我們什麼都不做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}也未免太說不過去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}是是 那個…那個…咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那兩個人已經走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}請您通融一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還剩下一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\fad(320,50)\c&H49465B&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(649,263)}有一件訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}莎拉小姐的回收已經完成了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果有興趣的話就回辦公室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們的工作也就全部告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:18:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們準備為你們開個小小的慰問會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當然也不用勉強非要來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管怎樣先優先處理你們自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算你們不來 我們也會HIGH起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然這樣說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}歡迎回來～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}歡迎～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們已經開始了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天的主角出現啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在公司裡喝酒真的沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事 沒事～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在這裡的全員都已經把工作提前完成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然康孝你好像只是睡了一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為了騰出今天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家可是拚命提前完成了工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為此大家上週都過得非常忙碌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管怎麼說 現在已經是非工作時間啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我允許你們飲酒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不 這是我允許的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可是為了得到許可 卑躬屈膝地求了部長好久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要老命了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你做的很好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來 兩位請拿好這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的 全員注意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這麼長時間以來 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼 乾杯囉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(251,142)\fsp0}香月就交給我吧。\N\N康斯坦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(337,335)}辛苦了。暫時忘掉工作，\N先考慮自己的幸福吧，好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(320,443)}啊，不介意的話，什麼時候\N來我房間裡玩都可以喲？\N滿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(460,570)}謝謝你總是泡茶給我們。\N非常好喝唷。\N山野邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(298,667)}再見囉～\N塞克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs30\c&H393939&\pos(711,137)}辛苦啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(877,142)}害羞了（笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp0\an9\fs30\c&H393939&\3c&HFAFCFC&\pos(782,433)}艾拉 辛苦啦~！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp0\an7\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(701,600)}艾拉醬LOVE\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h海松繪瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(1222,201)}第一終端服務課的友情永遠不滅！\N土器連
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(1250,341)}從現在開始盡情對喜歡的男生撒嬌吧。\N那樣的任性會被允許的。\N康孝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(1235,470)}與你一起共事是非常值得驕傲的一件事。\N雪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(1238,615)}單元測驗房會一直為你保留著的。\N右次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘿～嘿～加油～加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘿～嘿～加油～加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉好像很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒想到你們真的回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}發來信息的就是滿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然是那樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然嘴上這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說要開這個會的就是滿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 為什麼每次都要戳穿我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}來 接著喝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒什麼啊 反正我早就知道司是個需要別人照顧的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你笑什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.26,0:21:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你才是在笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才沒在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}笑啦 笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克你也這樣
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}累了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 好像有一點鬧過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事啦 沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得 雖然發生了許多事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是能在那裡工作真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能遇到大家 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.51,0:21:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在開心的 愉快的事太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多到日記裡都寫不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.66,0:21:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這些都是托司的福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可以問個問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天你對莎拉小姐說了些什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:21:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:22:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前 每次回收的最後你都一定會那樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.62,0:22:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我之前就很在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.79,0:22:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會想你都說了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「願你終將與重要的人再次相會」
